{"tid":441977,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"美國消費者報告　2017年度最佳手機排行榜　又係垃圾三星～","createTime":"2017-10-20T07:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T15:38:30.000Z","uid":141060,"like":10,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff64890a0ba0a33611efe68b11d5be6d98db3ae","tid":441977,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:39:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.consumerreports.org/smartphones/samsung-galaxy-s8-phones-top-consumer-reports-smartphone-ratings/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumerreports.org%2Fsmartphones%2Fsamsung-galaxy-s8-phones-top-consumer-reports-smartphone-ratings%2F&d=b2Y%2BkDJcXyKZZPO4JsRoT8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=e78e202f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.consumerreports.org/smartphones/samsung-galaxy-s8-phones-top-consumer-reports-smartphone-ratings/</a><br />\n<br />\n2017年度最佳手機排行榜出爐，iPhone8還不如去年的三星S7<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/20/153448_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2F153448_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=cdd2fd2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國權威網站《消費者報告》(Consumer Reports)台灣時間18日更新了2017年度最佳手機排行榜，但令人意外的是，冠軍寶座竟然不是剛開賣的iPhone8，而且iPhone8系列還輸給了三星的舊機，讓人跌破眼鏡。<br />\n占據排行榜第一、二名的分別是三星2017上半年的旗艦S8與S8+，然而第三名的則是三星去年的S7，第四、第五名才是iPhone8與8 plus，而三星的最新旗艦Note8則是僅獲得第六名的名次<br />\n<br />\n《消費者報告》創辦自 1936 年，是美國歷史悠久的非營利組織，旨在提供公正的消費資訊。此次排名讓人意外的，還包括上市 1 年半的 Galaxy S7 仍領先 iPhone 8，排在第三，三星的新旗艦 Galaxy Note 8，則反而排到第六。<br />\n<br />\n回顧 6 月《消費者報告》將 Galaxy S8 評為 2017 最佳手機的評語，包括嶄新的外型設計、強大的電池續航與頂級相機成像。值得注意的是，《消費者報告》的評價也頗在意 CP 值與手感重量，如 S8+ 之所以排到第二，便是因為重量與價格較高。Galaxy Note 8 亦因為手感重量與螢幕不耐摔被扣了分數，才來到第六。<br />\n<br />\n後續值得觀察的，還包括 iPhone X 正式上市後，《消費者報告》會不會更新手機評價或排名。Google Pixel 2 的評測亦還沒出爐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f88d0728fc4e5483ab75508ea021f258a2ff8d","tid":441977,"uid":12628,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾iphone8 就唔使講啦，三星的最新旗艦Note8 竟然不及s8,s8plus，甚至上年嘅S7, 睇黎三星真係愈黎愈退步了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3569abc6cc80a4720d1c791c666e92ab3e6763","tid":441977,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"推，等大家知三星s8才是機皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8af4c3effc41bc7bcb7cbc7cce34d3b20d17233","tid":441977,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"屌，我啲三星同事呢喂，唔入黎幫推？未放工架喎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95674394eee451568bb9460e1c833bf83cda1b19","tid":441977,"uid":65144,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:00:19.000Z","msg":"硬擦膠=3星打手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/424802/page/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/424802/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"3522d25996363430b49fccfdc80d1a294a83d74d","tid":441977,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>硬擦膠=3星打手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/424802/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/424802/page/1?ref=android</a></blockquote><br />\n屌老味，機皇S8唔推得？！"},{"pid":"8e2bd6f8bc799d16f871252dd432cf90685f3068","tid":441977,"uid":17103,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T09:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾iphone8 就唔使講啦，三星的最新旗艦Note8 竟然不及s8,s8plus，甚至上年嘅S7, 睇黎三星真係愈黎愈退步了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慘會唔會扣錢"},{"pid":"d34a3cb53964bdf8ebbc4ec579a17284713bddcc","tid":441977,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"